Prompt 2.2.2: Create Video Components
Objective: Build reusable video display components.
Instructions for AI Agent:

Create video-related components:

1. src/components/video/VideoCard.astro:
   - Accept props: video (Video type)
   - Display:
     - Thumbnail image (16:9 aspect ratio)
     - Duration badge (bottom-right of thumbnail)
     - Title (max 2 lines, truncate with ellipsis)
     - Uploader name with avatar
     - View count and upload date
     - Rating indicator (likes/dislikes or star rating)
   - Styling:
     - Card with subtle shadow
     - Hover effect: lift slightly, increase shadow
     - Cursor pointer
     - Rounded corners
   - Link to /video/[id] page
   - Mobile responsive

2. src/components/video/VideoGrid.astro:
   - Accept props: videos (Video[])
   - Display videos in responsive grid:
     - Mobile: 1 column
     - Tablet: 2-3 columns
     - Desktop: 4-5 columns
   - Gap between cards: 1.5rem
   - Use VideoCard component for each video

3. src/components/video/VideoPlayer.astro:
   - Accept props: video (Video type)
   - Display:
     - HTML5 video player or placeholder for now
     - Video controls (play, pause, volume, fullscreen, progress bar)
     - For mockup: just show poster image with play button overlay
   - Aspect ratio: 16:9
   - Width: 100% of container
   - Max width: 1280px
   - Add note: "Video player will be functional when connected to backend"

4. src/components/ui/Pagination.astro:
   - Accept props: pagination (PaginationData type)
   - Display:
     - Previous button
     - Page numbers (show current, 2 before, 2 after)
     - Next button
     - Total results count
   - Styling:
     - Centered
     - Current page highlighted
     - Disabled state for prev/next when applicable
   - For mockup: buttons use # links

   

DELIVERABLE: Complete video components with clean, functional UI.